+| `CTX_FRAMEWORK_ROOT` | daemon | Framework repo root |
+| `CTX_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID` | agent .env | Your Telegram chat ID |
+| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | shell profile | Never stored in a file |
